N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 154.4 - Effective date

State Regulations

The provisions of this Part are to be effective January 1, 1985. Moving or relocation expenses incurred by management/confidential
employees prior to January 1, 1985 are covered by the regulations in place at
that time. Notes
